            "Invalid request: invalid type: null, expected a string"
        )

        let resourceInvalidThreadType = try appServerResponse(
            #"{"id":7,"method":"mcpServer/resource/read","params":{"threadId":1,"server":"filesystem","uri":"file:///tmp/a"}}"#,
            codexHome: temp.url
